Summary: The document outlines a learning journey at OCBC Centre on Chulia Street, organized by NUS Institute of Systems Science (NUS-ISS). The purpose of the journey is to gain insights into the technologies and work of the Al Lab and Group Data Office teams at OCBC. Participants will have the opportunity to meet with various teams, including HR Business Partners and Talent Acquisition, and learn about personalized mentorship and regional networking opportunities at OCBC.
